      "uuid": "cbce95a8985e4b36a665755b0ad1f3d8",
      "type": "warm",
      "title": "In the land of Thurr",
      "full_text": "During an architectural expedition machines where discovered.  \n\nMachines that someone had created with intent to destroy the world.  \n\nNone of the expedition members returned except the professor who managed to flee and take refuge in Japan.  The professor had one goal and one goal only, to use his two greatest discoveries, the elusive organic matter and the invincible machine, to oppose this attempt at disrupting the beautiful status quo.",
      "pos_x": 285.8901354876738,
      "pos_y": -544.8851560412842,
      "width": 538.6399451974717,
      "height": 264.0,
      "ports_visible": false
    },
    {
      "node_id": 4,
      "uuid": "7c6bae16bf82461da7789e999374d78a",
      "type": "warm",
      "title": "The humans tried acquiring it",
      "full_text": "We must have it!  It will let us rule the world!!  Our armies will be invincible! They shouted.",
